This state is a very condensed version of
about 10,000 different eco systems and you

00:05:03.449 --> 00:05:12.199
can go experience a whole lot of them even
in one day - going from the coast to the mountains,

00:05:12.199 --> 00:05:13.919
to the high desert.

00:05:13.919 --> 00:05:20.770
It's a phenomenal place to live and recreate
and enjoy ourselves.

00:05:20.770 --> 00:05:27.749
And I think we all know it and yet what we
don't really remember all the time is how

00:05:27.749 --> 00:05:35.469
diversity of different landscapes makes Oregon
such an incredible place.

00:05:35.469 --> 00:05:40.529
'Cause it's now just all mountains, it's not
